original_title: Bronx: West Farms Road - 172nd Street & 174th Street
text:
West Farms Road, east side, between E. 172nd and E. 174th Streets, showing one of buildings of the Northern Union Gas Company and a number of shacks.

P. L. Sperr

May 31, 1928
